payload.text:
To satisfy your request to add themes that match the visual styles provided in the images (specifically Retrowave/Synthwave, Watercolor, Bokeh, and Abstract Waves), I will add 4 new themes: **Retrowave**, **Watercolor**, **Bokeh**, and **Nebula**.

I will also implement a specialized dynamic SVG background generator for each of these themes so they closely resemble the backgrounds in your images (e.g., the grid and sun for Retrowave, soft blobs for Watercolor, circles for Bokeh).

# Updated files:

## App.tsx

```tsx
